rem Old Man
rem 8/29/2017

ifflag oldman name
 [|
  do Ask Name
   [
    print "I am who they need me to be, yes... You understand."
    setflag oldman name
   ]
 ]

do Ask About City
 [
  print "This city is a trap, it will try to suck the life out of you, never letting
  print you go. Only through Zen can you find a way out."
  setflag know zen
 ]

do Ask About Hotel
 [
  ifflag ask hotel
   [
    print "I've done it, I've left the hotel only to find Insectoids that live in their
    print own futuristic world."
   |
    print "This place is parallel vortex, through those tubes, the sleeping chambers,
    print you can enter other dimensions."
    setflag ask hotel
   ]  
 ]

ifflag know zen
 [
  do Ask About Zen
   [
    ifflag ask zen
     [
      print "Once your mind is quiet you will see the true state of things. We live in
      print a simulation."
      setflag know simulation
     |
      print "Zen shows you the state of things. Quiet the mind and it will show you
      print wonders." 
      setflag ask zen
     ]
   ]
 |]

ifflag know simulation
 [
  do Ask About Simulation
   [
    ifflag ask simulation
     [
      print "I know the answer, but you not understand. You must quiet your own mind."
      print
      print "The lesson is done," he says with a clap of his hands, getting up, leaving
      print the hotel pass behind. Before you can say anything he walks out of the hotel.
      setflag oldman gone
      create hotel pass,Cheap Hotel
      go Cheap Hotel
     |
      print "Yes, yes. I'm sure you agree. We have to live in a simulation, this whole
      print world seems like a storybook construct. But the question is why are we here?
      print What do we need to learn from all this?"
      setflag ask simulation
     ]
   ]
 |]

do End Conversation
 [
  print You leave the old man to his strange ideas.
  go Cheap Hotel
 ]

